title: #92Noon! Florio/Kyndra/McGinest/Gleeman/Burns
description: Talkers to start 92Noon, then Florio finishes first hour! FSN Loons analyst Kyndra de St Aubin in studio to pump up Minnesota United FC's playoff game, Willie McGinest calls in to chat NFL, then Gleeman is in studio with hardcore baseball opinions. Ryan Burns looks ahead to Gophers/Rutgers to wrap the show~!
